{"tid":1064878,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【比卡超】【國歌法】廖長江柒少陣啦，咪拉埋德國落水","createTime":"2019-03-17T00:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T05:20:53.000Z","uid":138409,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7acf101c1b2a0ba1b5e319d4de376dbabf22bf66","tid":1064878,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T00:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0sk34JO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0sk34JO.gif&h=a2d5ffef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/2136960963083843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEdInDisguise%2Fposts%2F2136960963083843&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQkwXckNDuUEQQ0Md4EdtPbyE%3D&h=fbc67f39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/2136960963083843</a><br />\nNok Hin Au問政府，政權懲罰市民侮辱國歌係咪國際標準<br />\n<br />\n鄧忍光無辦法，只能夠話無咁樣既國際標準，承認政府而家只係盲從緊全國性法律，反正罰則跟返《國旗及國徽條例》，所以無問題blah blah blah<br />\n<br />\n廖長江突然間插嘴，話區議員你可以參考下德國，佢地侮辱國歌的罰則同香港好接近<br />\n<br />\n係都要衝出來柒既<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">誠然，德國《刑法典(Strafgesetzbuch)》第90a(1)(2)條確實禁止任何人公開誹謗（verunglimpft）德國國旗、國徽或國歌（或聯邦州的旗徽歌）</span>，違者最高可被判3年監禁。<br />\n<br />\n但德國聯邦憲法法院自1990年兩宗分別涉及侮辱國旗和侮辱國歌的案件開始，就已經考慮到第90a(1)(2)條實際上限制了德國《基本法 (Grundgesetz)》第5(1)條所保障的藝術自由和言論自由，<span style=\"color: gold;\">所以「誹謗」的含義不可過分寬泛</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果國歌或國旗只是媒介，對國歌或國旗的侮辱實際上是為了表達某個信息（尤其是政治信息）的話，相關表達行為即構成行使表達自由，而非第90a(1)(2)條意義下的「誹謗」</span>：參見BVerfGE 81, 278 (7 March 1990) at II(3); BVerfGE 81, 298 (7 March 1990) at B(I)(3); 1 BvR 1565/05 (15 September 2008) at III(3)。這是因為德國法律並不強制公民接受憲法所反映的價值；公民有自由質疑憲法背後的基本判斷，或要求修改憲法的基本原則。 德國《基本法》的多元精神相信整個社會有能力處理和成功回應對憲法的批評：參見 1 BvR 1565/05 (15 September 2008) at III(3)。<br />\n<br />\n在更近期的判決中，聯邦憲法法院解釋，<span style=\"color: gold;\">國家和一般公民不同，並無享有「個人榮譽」的基本權利，反而作為憲政制度的一部份，必須時刻忍受尖銳批評。</span>因此，聯邦憲法法院裁定，除非相關的侮辱具體地去到一個危及德國存在、或危害國家機構運作或德國和平的程度，否則不可以《刑法典》第90a條懲罰公民侮辱國家，以免違反公民受憲法保障的基本權利：1 BvR 917/09 (28 November 2011 ) at II(2)(b)(bb)。"},{"pid":"d980d646e319999dd78e66b1d2badbfb126ad1d7","tid":1064878,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T00:45:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"11ac601515bccbe8e8c3fe8a4dea73f356a8cbd1","tid":1064878,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T00:47:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1d011737aa6cad0bff6629c8b0431b8e1d58d3dd","tid":1064878,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T00:54:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1533229b8221ca8e74e9d44f9fda27dc746f2d0f","tid":1064878,"uid":138409,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:05:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同場加映</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/2136509323129007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEdInDisguise%2Fposts%2F2136509323129007&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQkwXckNDuUEQQ0Md4EdtPbyE%3D&h=846832ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/2136509323129007</a><br />\n聽到公聽會有建制派動員出黎既人話<span style=\"color: purple;\">英國</span>、<span style=\"color: teal;\">法國</span>同<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">美國</span>幾個「所謂西方民主國家」都有國歌法，所以國歌法是國際標準云云<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先<span style=\"color: purple;\">英國</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">係無任何國歌法</span>的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；god save the queen／king只係歷史流傳下來的傳統，並無法律基礎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">法國</span>的《刑法典》禁止侮辱國歌，但只限於在官方舉辦的活動中所作的侮辱，雖然如果你問我，其實在官方活動中侮辱國歌反而先最有意義，<span style=\"color: gold;\">但至少法國法律並無限制市民在日常生活中 － 尤其是在示威遊行中 －公開對國家象徵表達不滿甚至鄙視</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">美國</span>就更加添啦，最高法院於Texas v Johnson, 491 US 397 (1989)；United States v Eichman, 496 US 310 (1990)兩單案件中認為，<span style=\"color: gold;\">禁止市民侮辱國家象徵甚至侮辱整個憲制，等於強迫市民尊重國家，是不文明的做法，有違言論自由和思想自由的精神，違反美國憲法第一修正案</span><br />\n<br />\n下次做好啲啲research先出來9up，唔該～"},{"pid":"3b8c3019075022baedb03e48f1449e2e9c0946f8","tid":1064878,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5250ec8b5a6b09b902fa8a59cf1d5fb47aabc1f7","tid":1064878,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:12:31.000Z","msg":"Edward Wong:<br />\n<br />\n補充返，法國《刑法典》第433-5-1條所指「 由公共當局規管的場合(manifestations r&eacute;glement&eacute;es par les autorit&eacute;s publiques) 」，是指體育、娛樂或文化性質的公眾活動，主要考量是因在場人數眾多而產生的衛生或保安風險<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">其他政治性的活動，即使由官方舉辦，應也不受該條所限</span>"},{"pid":"0f2ba395f042aa35170d00f138ee75c79432bb9e","tid":1064878,"uid":161185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:22:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"316b0491b75fff3b659b5ed0f3aca6122887145b","tid":1064878,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"高質po"},{"pid":"5c1b77155c3ceb8352170f9699464efdbc97465a","tid":1064878,"uid":51308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:34:38.000Z","msg":"高質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3f0300f4bdf88ee01599a75fed8ca7493abee0","tid":1064878,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:36:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ee677569412c570a73d69f6c686fda43f3d1dd7a","tid":1064878,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:36:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29c0e0425a8900829d41a9be07b0fd072540ea72","tid":1064878,"uid":136431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:40:13.000Z","msg":"聯邦憲法法院解釋，國家和一般公民不同，並無享有「個人榮譽」的基本權利，反而作為憲政制度的一部份，必須時刻忍受尖銳批評。<br />\n<br />\n中國連嗰兩句批評都頂唔住，仲要習維尼朕即國家，想搬日耳曼出嚟，貽笑大方。成撚日自己想做咩閪嘢，就話咩外國都係咁乜乜柒柒，扮撚晒嘢拋書包，又淨係知面嗰浸，越搞自己越撚柒"},{"pid":"8b48dd30eb6ed44ca14986a6818a3001b95f9c5a","tid":1064878,"uid":136431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1533229b8221ca8e74e9d44f9fda27dc746f2d0f","tid":1064878,"uid":138409,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:05:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同場加映</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/2136509323129007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEdInDisguise%2Fposts%2F2136509323129007&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQkwXckNDuUEQQ0Md4EdtPbyE%3D&h=846832ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/2136509323129007</a><br />\n聽到公聽會有建制派動員出黎既人話<span style=\"color: purple;\">英國</span>、<span style=\"color: teal;\">法國</span>同<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">美國</span>幾個「所謂西方民主國家」都有國歌法，所以國歌法是國際標準云云<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先<span style=\"color: purple;\">英國</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">係無任何國歌法</span>的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；god save the queen／king只係歷史流傳下來的傳統，並無法律基礎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">法國</span>的《刑法典》禁止侮辱國歌，但只限於在官方舉辦的活動中所作的侮辱，雖然如果你問我，其實在官方活動中侮辱國歌反而先最有意義，<span style=\"color: gold;\">但至少法國法律並無限制市民在日常生活中 － 尤其是在示威遊行中 －公開對國家象徵表達不滿甚至鄙視</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">美國</span>就更加添啦，最高法院於Texas v Johnson, 491 US 397 (1989)；United States v Eichman, 496 US 310 (1990)兩單案件中認為，<span style=\"color: gold;\">禁止市民侮辱國家象徵甚至侮辱整個憲制，等於強迫市民尊重國家，是不文明的做法，有違言論自由和思想自由的精神，違反美國憲法第一修正案</span><br />\n<br />\n下次做好啲啲research先出來9up，唔該～"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:59:01.000Z","msg":"人哋行憲政，維護公民言論自由，都係國際標準。又唔見班KINA人 講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9f412b3f84bad71cc6147b6e287e8460ffe716","tid":1064878,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:06:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"478a4c7dc34ec2dcdfdb76ae946557d6d3fa32a4","tid":1064878,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef2135b3ac437bea1502a32b6abef2e605c37f7","tid":1064878,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只提法例就不提細則<br />\n重有個仆街話支那進行曲係好歌朗朗上口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa746804e72b723e44334164f66a6c3fe26a4d4","tid":1064878,"uid":149662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"推俾多啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65c785aaf5e1bbd95d352d78190572c720b169f","tid":1064878,"uid":128761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"先唔講德國唔係咁<br />\n班撚樣好搞笑既係平時最鍾意反歐美<br />\n但當佢地誤解左歐美有d咩係有利於佢哋時<br />\n就會話人地歐美都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}